summary: For Finley O'Connor love comes second, much to her mother’s dismay. For Harry Styles, life couldn’t revolve without love. When...
body:
For Finley O'Connor love comes second, much to her mother’s dismay. For Harry Styles, life couldn’t revolve without love. When the pair are set up on a blind date, they make a pact to help each other get the thing that is apparently missing from their lives. But how long will it take for them to realise what truly is missing?

A story about being 23, blind dates, and finding who you truly are.

summary: UMMMMM HOW DO YOU THINK MOB HARRY WOULD BE WHEN HIS DAUGHTER LEAVES FOR SCHOOL FOR THE VERY FIRST TIME :(( LIKE WOULD HE BE...
question: UMMMMM HOW DO YOU THINK MOB HARRY WOULD BE WHEN HIS DAUGHTER LEAVES FOR SCHOOL FOR THE VERY FIRST TIME :(( LIKE WOULD HE BE UPSET?? EXCITED??
answer:
excited and nervous and sad!!

harry literally swears that his little baby bub was just born yesterday and it hasn’t been four years since and today’s not the day that she first goes to school.

he’ll be all sulky preparing her snack and packing it in her lunchbox the both of them picked out and taking a picture of her and the missus beaming and seeing her pick put her own outfit??

i’d imagine him to be the one who’s distracting her so she’d have the reason to stay, but no, because her baby’s so smart that she doesn’t fall for it this time and figures it out without her mummy’s clues.

“really want to leave your daddy huh, princess?”

harry even pulls the guilt card that makes his daughter giggle that it makes his baby playfully shove him while he’s squatted down to her height, the three of them just a few steps away from the main entrance of her preschool.

“jus’ a couple of hours.”

“g’nna let mummy and daddy take you out later?”

she’s almost a carbon copy of him as she pretends to think, nodding her head eagerly later as he succumbs to both her parents’ hugs that were tighter than usual, smiling to them brightly as she did.

“m’kay.”
